    <tr>
      <td>
        <a name="service"></a>
        <h4>LOGO PRINTING ON RIBBON</h4><br>

        <span style="  color: #bdc3c7;"></span>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>
        <div class="line-separator"></div>
      </td>
    </tr>

    <tr>
      <td class="format_td">
        Put Your Logo On Ribbon. A Great Marketing Tool for packaging your products.
        Most Retailers are using custom printed logos on ribbon to gift wrap or package their items, and
        for displays and advertising. This is a colorful addition to any product and will implant your company
        name in the mind of your customers. It creates a unique & elegant look for your product, and
        can be applied to almost any type of packaging, including handles on a shopping bag.
        <br>
        As a supplier of commercial ribbon printing services, be advised that we do require a minimum
        order commitment of one thousand yards for most print methods and a three-thousand yard minimum
        for heat transfer printing.
        <br>
        Most of our custom ribbon logo printing is done on single or double faced satin to provide the best
        coverage. We can also print on grosgrain & sheer ribbon. Inks can be matched to Pantone colors,
        as well as standard colors.
        <br>
        There is a one time charge to create a printing plate. Artwork must be supplied on a clean "black &
        white" copy, properly sized and showing step and repeat. Artwork that is supplied on disk or
        electronically also must be sized exactly to be printed showing all repeats, in high resolution. For
        multiple color print jobs colors must be separated.
        <br>
        Our custom printing specialists will be pleased to discuss our various printing services with you.
        <br>
        <br>
        See “Custom Printing Information” for our various print methods.
      </td>
