    <tr>
      <td class="format_td">
        Our custom “made to order” bows can be produced from any pattern of ribbon we sell. Accessories
        such as a twist tie, double sided stick tape, or rubber bands can be placed on the back of the
        knot for adherence to your product. When you call, give us the exact measurements for the
        “head” of the bow, which is measured across the loops from one end to the other, and the “tail” of
        the bow, measured from the knot down to the longest point of one of the tails. We offer both hand
        tied and machine tied bows. Hand tied bows have a minimum order of 25 dozen per pattern. Machine
        tied bows, in a variety of smaller sizes, are pre-packaged in 5 gross bags.
